%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mexico%20poll%20frontrunner%20deluged%20with%20hate%20messages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708872174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE9B9%2Fproduction%2F_132733895_11c93a5342f816ac2afb60b85b432218c4ef23290_0_3316_22111000x667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68397627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Claudia%20Sheinbaum%2C%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20President%20L%C3%B3pez%20Obrador%2C%20has%20had%20her%20phone%20number%20leaked%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68397627%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68397627.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68397627.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ED%20summons%20Niranjan%20Hiranandani%2C%20son%20Darshan%20on%20Monday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708871506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107988752%2Cimgsize-25352.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fed-summons-niranjan-hiranandani-and-son-darshan-for-alleged-fema-rule-violation%2Farticleshow%2F107988722.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20summoned%20builder%20Niranjan%20Hiranandani%20and%20his%20son%20Darshan%20for%20alleged%20violation%20of%20FEMA%20rules.%20The%20investigation%20focuses%20on%20the%20offshore%20trust%2C%20misuse%20of%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%2C%20violation%20of%20FDI%20norms%2C%20non-performing%20asset%20declaration%2C%20and%20offshore%20entities%20in%20the%20British%20Virgin%20Islands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22VIJAY%20V%20SINGH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fed-summons-niranjan-hiranandani-and-son-darshan-for-alleged-fema-rule-violation%2Farticleshow%2F107988722.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Might%20the%20Congress-Samajwadi%20Party%20Alliance%20Achieve%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25161348%2FGHLSQf0aYAAENH-.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20division%20of%20seats%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20announced%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20February%2022%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20becomes%20the%20first%20major%20alliance%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20declare%20seats%20for%20each%20partner.%20The%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20surprisingly%20seems%20to%20be%20legging%20behind%20in%20dividing%20seats%20between%20its%20partners%20%E2%80%93%20the%20SBSP%20led%20by%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20the%20NISHAD%20party%20led%20by%20Sanjay%20Nishad%2C%20Apna%20Dal%20led%20by%20Anupriya%20Patel%20and%20RLD%20led%20by%20Jayant%20Chaudhary.%20Amidst%20the%20rumours%20of%20Jayant%20Chaudhry%E2%80%99s%20disgruntlement%20with%20the%20seat%20sharing%20in%20NDA%2C%20two%20significant%20questions%20have%20come%20up%3A%20what%20prompted%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20in%20UP%2C%20and%20what%20can%20it%20achieve%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectoral%20compulsions%20and%20ideological%20similarities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20election%20debacles%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20and%20later%20urban%20body%20elections%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20coined%20the%20formula%20of%20a%20PDA%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EPichda%2C%20Dalit%2C%20Alpasankhyak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Backwards%2C%20Dalits%2C%20Minorities)%20alliance.%20While%20voting%20patterns%20of%20past%20elections%20show%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20its%20allies%20still%20command%20a%20sizeable%20share%20of%20votes%20of%20non-Yadav%20OBCs%20and%20non-Jatav%20Dalits%20in%20UP%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20realised%20that%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20section%20of%20these%20communities%20who%20are%20getting%20disenchanted%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Factors%20like%20agrarian%20issues%2C%20inflation%20and%20joblessness%20among%20these%20communities%20were%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20major%20forces%20behind%20this.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20party%20prepared%20a%20strategy%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20communities%20at%20the%20booth%20level%20and%20establish%20a%20direct%20connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20similar%20lines%20albeit%20much%20earlier%20and%20on%20an%20all-India%20level%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20first%20launched%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20later%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20to%20galvanise%20anti-BJP%20sentiment%20among%20these%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CCongress%20has%20been%20consistently%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20census%2C%20socio-economic%20justice%20and%20joblessness.%20The%20two%20yatras%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20have%20attempted%20to%20make%20the%20Dalit-OBC%20population%20of%20the%20country%20realise%20that%20their%20future%20is%20not%20safe%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20UP%20Congress%20general%20secretary%20Anil%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Congress-SP%20Alliance%20Seals%20Seat-Sharing%20Deal%20in%20UP%20and%20MP%2C%20but%20Some%20Major%20Challenges%20Remain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-sp-alliance-seals-seat-sharing-deal-in-up-and-mp-but-some-major-challenges-remain%5C%22%3ECongress-SP%20Alliance%20Seals%20Seat-Sharing%20Deal%20in%20UP%20and%20MP%2C%20but%20Some%20Major%20Challenges%20Remain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20SP%20succeed%20in%20getting%20majority%20of%20Muslim%20and%20Yadav%20votes%20in%202022%20as%20per%20CSDS%20data%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so%20successful%20in%20attracting%20Dalit%20and%20other%20OBC%20voters%2C%20due%20to%20it%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20Muslim-Yadav%20party.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20past%20surveys%20done%20by%20People%E2%80%99s%20Pulse%20in%20UP%20indicate%20that%20despite%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%E2%80%99s%20positive%20image%2C%20these%20communities%20did%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20the%20perception%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20in%20the%20fight%20in%20the%20bi-polar%202022%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20both%20parties%20now%20coming%20together%20in%20an%20alliance%2C%20these%20shortcomings%20could%20be%20overcome.%20While%20the%20Congress%20can%20soften%20the%20image%20of%20the%20SP%20and%20widen%20the%20vote%20base%20of%20the%20party%2C%20the%20SP%20can%20increase%20the%20winnability%20perception%20of%20the%20former%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lucknow-based%20veteran%20journalist%20Siddharth%20Kalhans.%20It%20is%20also%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%202022%20surveys%20indicated%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20Muslim%20voters%20were%20clearly%20saying%20that%20though%20in%202022%20they%20are%20voting%20for%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%2C%20they%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%202024.%20The%20SP%20was%20wary%20of%20losing%20them%20in%20a%20crucial%20election%20like%202024.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20therefore%20seems%20that%20electoral%20compulsions%20and%20similar%20ideological%20goals%20perhaps%20brought%20the%20two%20parties%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20sums%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20can%20the%20alliance%20achieve%20in%20UP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20while%20passing%20through%20UP%2C%20attracted%20huge%20crowds%20and%20was%20joined%20by%20SP%20leaders%20and%20cadres%20alike.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20incumbent%20UP%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-recruitment-exam-cancelled-bjp-yields-to-pressure-amid-paper-leak-allegations-protests%5C%22%3Eis%20facing%20the%20ire%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20unemployed%20youth%20protesting%20against%20paper%20leaks%20in%20constable%20and%20RO%2FARO%20recruitment%20exams.%20Amidst%20these%20developments%2C%20some%20experts%20feel%20that%20the%20euphoria%20and%20positive%20atmosphere%20that%20the%20BJP%20created%20through%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20in%20early%20January%20seems%20to%20be%20subsiding.%20But%20will%20this%20mean%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20can%20properly%20challenge%20the%20NDA%20in%202024%20in%20UP%2C%20bringing%20down%20its%20numbers%20from%2064%20(62%20to%20BJP%20and%20two%20to%20Apna%20Dal%20Sonelal)%20in%202019%3F%20A%20closer%20look%20at%20the%20data%20of%20past%20elections%20and%20current%20trends%20might%20give%20us%20a%20clearer%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20understanding%20is%20that%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20led%20by%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20election%20was%20more%20than%2038.5%25%2C%20if%20we%20include%20the%20Congress.%20This%20amounts%20to%20approximately%2030%20out%20of%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20vote%20percentage%20alone%20does%20not%20amount%20to%20seats%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20first-past-the-post%20system.%20A%20party%20could%20be%20getting%20votes%20across%20a%20state%20which%20might%20look%20impressive%20in%20total%2C%20and%20yet%20fail%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat.%20The%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20UP%20during%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20this%2C%20as%20the%20party%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20despite%20polling%2019.77%25%20of%20the%20total%20votes.%20In%20this%20scenario%2C%20the%20seats%20won%2Fleads%20logic%20appears%20more%20appropriate%20to%20make%20a%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20India%20Alliance%20May%20Not%20Be%20as%20Dead%20After%20All%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-india-alliance-may-not-be-as-dead-after-all%5C%22%3EThe%20India%20Alliance%20May%20Not%20Be%20as%20Dead%20After%20All%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20seats%20won%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20(including%20the%20Congress)%20collectively%20led%20in%20127%20assembly%20segments%20which%20also%20roughly%20converts%20to%20around%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20(as%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20is%20made%20of%20five%20assembly%20seats%20in%20UP%2C%20generally).%20By%20this%20logic%2C%20the%20NDA%20could%20be%20limited%20to%20around%2055%20seats%20in%20the%202024%20elections%20by%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20which%20is%20far%20less%20than%20the%2064%20it%20won%20in%202019.%20But%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20contested%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Apna%20Dal%20and%20Nishad%20Party%20only%2C%20and%20now%20it%20also%20has%20the%20support%20of%20the%20SBSP%20and%20RLD%2C%20who%20jumped%20sides%20after%20the%20elections.%20Adding%20their%20numbers%20to%20the%20NDA%20seat%20tally%20of%202022%20results%20in%20the%20saffron%20alliance%20jumping%20to%20287%20seats%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20around%2058%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20can%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20limit%20the%20BJP%20to%20even%20those%20numbers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENarrative%2C%20social%20engineering%20and%20political%20churn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20shortcomings%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20currently%20the%20most%20prepared%20party%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20with%20enormous%20organisational%20and%20government%20machinery%20and%20huge%20financial%20resources%20at%20its%20disposal.%20Major%20surveys%20show%20that%20though%20the%20popularity%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20increased%2C%20that%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20still%20unmatchable.%20Further%2C%20its%20narrative%20of%20%E2%80%9CRam%2C%20Roti%20and%20Rashtra%E2%80%9D%20(Hindutva%2C%20beneficiary%20policies%20and%20hyper%20nationalism)%20has%20still%20not%20lost%20its%20shine%2C%20despite%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20in%20UP%2C%20it%20has%20always%20been%20a%20battle%20between%20social%20engineering%20and%20narrative.%20And%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20seems%20to%20have%20taken%20the%20first%20step%20to%20carve%20out%20a%20greater%20social%20base%2C%20charged%20with%20an%20anti-BJP%20narrative.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%2012%20years%20since%20the%20BSP%20lost%20power%20in%20UP%20and%20it%20has%20not%20recovered%20since%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rama%20Shankar%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20Ambedkar%20University%20Delhi%20and%20the%20author%20of%20a%20book%20on%20UP%E2%80%99s%20EBCs.%20%E2%80%9CA%20large%20section%20of%20the%20BSP%20vote%20base%20%E2%80%93%20Dalits%20and%20EBCs%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20disgruntled%20is%20definitely%20available%20and%20trying%20to%20find%20new%20political%20options.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20he%20also%20cautions%20that%20the%20voting%20memory%20of%20these%20groups%20for%20Congress%20is%20very%20old%20and%20they%20have%20not%20liked%20the%20SP%20due%20to%20a%20history%20of%20social%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20above%20factors%2C%20what%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20will%20achieve%20will%20greatly%20depend%20on%20the%20right%20messaging%2C%20better%20candidates%20and%20creating%20a%20larger%20social%20base.%20With%20a%20freefall%20in%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20situation%20in%20UP%20and%20its%20absence%20from%20all%20major%20political%20interventions%20and%20issues%2C%20various%20social%20blocs%20and%20castes%20previously%20loyal%20to%20it%20are%20looking%20for%20options.%20If%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20succeeds%20in%20creating%20a%20broadened%20social%20base%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20to%20at%20least%20stop%20the%20BJP%20from%20gaining%20in%20UP%20above%20the%202019%20numbers%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20that%20would%20be%20no%20small%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708871455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F25161348%2FGHLSQf0aYAAENH-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-might-the-congress-samajwadi-party-alliance-achieve-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20will%20achieve%20will%20greatly%20depend%20on%20the%20right%20messaging%2C%20better%20candidates%20and%20creating%20a%20larger%20social%20base.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-might-the-congress-samajwadi-party-alliance-achieve-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20INLD%20Chief%20Shot%20Dead%2C%20His%20SUV%20Was%20Ambushed%20By%20Gunmen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENafe%20Singh%20Rathi%2C%20Haryana%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20president%20and%20former%20MLA%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20this%20evening%20by%20unidentified%20gunmen%20who%20ambushed%20the%20SUV%20he%20was%20travelling%20by%20in%20Jhajjar%20district.%20Two%20others%20who%20were%20travelling%20with%20him%20have%20also%20died%20while%20two%20others%20are%20critically%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathi%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20inside%20the%20vehicle%20when%20the%20men%2C%20who%20came%20in%20a%20car%2C%20opened%20fire.%20The%20attackers%20fled%20the%20scene%20after%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20injured%20were%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20closeby%20Brahm%20Shakti%20Sanjivani%20Hospital%20for%20medical%20treatment%20but%20the%20former%20MLA%20was%20declared%20dead%20on%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20Sihag%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20INLD's%20media%20cell%2C%20confirmed%20Nafe%20Singh%20Rathi's%20death%20in%20the%20shootout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENafe%20Singh%20Rathi%20served%20as%20an%20MLA%20of%20the%20INLD%20from%20Bahadurgarh%20where%20the%20attack%20took%20place.%20The%20state%20police%20is%20on%20alert%20after%20the%20shocking%20attack.%20Several%20teams%20have%20been%20swiftly%20mobilised%20to%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crime%20and%20are%20collecting%20evidence%20to%20ascertain%20the%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20attack.%20Authorities%20are%20reviewing%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20various%20locations%20in%20the%20vicinity%20to%20determine%20the%20route%20of%20the%20attacker's%20arrival%20and%20their%20subsequent%20escape%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20and%20his%20close%20associate%20Kala%20Jathedi%20are%20suspected%20to%20be%20behind%20the%20attack.%20Initial%20inquiries%20suggest%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20due%20to%20a%20property%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENafe%20Singh%20Rathi%20has%20a%20prominent%20political%20background%2C%20having%20served%20twice%20as%20a%20legislator%20in%20the%20Haryana%20Legislative%20Assembly.%20He%20was%20also%20the%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Haryana%20Former%20Legislators%20Association.%20Rathi%20once%20contested%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20Rohtak%20constituency%20and%20had%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20political%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20served%20twice%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Bahadurgarh%20Municipal%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20name%20hit%20headlines%20last%20year%20when%20former%20Haryana%20minister%20Mange%20Ram%20Rathi's%20son%20Jagdish%20Rathi%20died%20by%20suicide%20and%20a%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20Nafe%20Singh%20Rathi%20under%20the%20charges%20of%20abetment.%20Allegations%20of%20harassment%20were%20subsequently%20leveled%20against%20Rathi%20and%20his%20nephew%20Sonu%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20suicide%20case.%20Rathi%20was%20granted%20anticipatory%20bail%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20on%20January%2024%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708871340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fplg82sfg_nafe-singh-rathi_625x300_25_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-inld-chief-nafe-singh-rathi-shot-dead-his-suv-was-ambushed-by-gunmen-5125465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nafe%20Singh%20Rathi%2C%20Haryana%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20president%20and%20former%20MLA%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20this%20evening%20by%20unidentified%20gunmen%20who%20ambushed%20the%20SUV%20he%20was%20travelling%20by%20in%20Jhajjar%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-inld-chief-nafe-singh-rathi-shot-dead-his-suv-was-ambushed-by-gunmen-5125465%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-inld-chief-nafe-singh-rathi-shot-dead-his-suv-was-ambushed-by-gunmen-5125465%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-inld-chief-nafe-singh-rathi-shot-dead-his-suv-was-ambushed-by-gunmen-5125465%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20Guarantee%20Begins%20From%20Where%20Hope%20Ends%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20Inaugurates%205%20AIIMS%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDevelopment%20was%20taking%20place%20under%20his%20government%20at%20a%20rate%20many%20times%20faster%20than%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20six%20to%20seven%20decades%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20on%20Sunday%2C%20and%20emphasised%20that%20his%20guarantee%20begins%20from%20where%20hope%20ends%20from%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20after%20inaugurating%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20in%20Rajkot%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Bathinda%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Raebareli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Kalyani%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Mangalagiri%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20function%20held%20here%2C%20the%20PM%20also%20dedicated%20to%20the%20nation%20various%20development%20works%20costing%20Rs%2048%2C000%20crore%2C%20including%20more%20than%20200%20health%20care%20infrastructure%20projects%20costing%20Rs%2011%2C500%20crore%20in%2023%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi's%20guarantee%20begins%20from%20where%20hope%20ends%20from%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20the%20country%20was%20saying%20this%20looking%20at%20the%20pace%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%2050%20years%20after%20Independence%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20AIIMS%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20that%20too%20in%20Delhi.%20In%20the%20seven%20decades%20since%20Independence%2C%20only%20seven%20AIIMS%20were%20approved%20but%20even%20these%20were%20never%20completed%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20swipe%20at%20previous%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20in%20just%2010%20days%2C%20seven%20new%20AIIMS%20were%20either%20inaugurated%20or%20their%20foundation%20stones%20laid.%20That's%20why%20I%20am%20saying%20that%20we%20are%20developing%20the%20country%20many%20times%20faster%20than%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20last%20six%20to%20seven%20decades%20and%20are%20dedicating%20it%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20the%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20people%20from%20different%20states%20used%20to%20get%20tired%20seeking%20AIIMS%20in%20their%20areas%20from%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20whereas%20today%20modern%20hospitals%20and%20medical%20facilities%20like%20AIIMS%20are%20opening%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20he%20had%20fulfilled%20his%20guarantee%20of%20setting%20up%20a%20large%20number%20of%20AIIMS%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20his%20government%20had%20approved%2010%20AIIMS%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20given%20a%20guarantee%20of%20(setting%20up)%20AIIMS%20to%20UP's%20Raebareli.%20The%20royal%20family%20of%20Congress%20only%20indulged%20in%20politics%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20while%20the%20work%20was%20done%20by%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20managed%20to%20defeat%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20because%20of%20changes%20in%20the%20health%20care%20system%20brought%20about%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20in%20Rajkot%20we%20got%20a%20glimpse%20of%20how%20the%20health%20sector%20of%20the%20world's%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20should%20be%20and%20what%20will%20be%20the%20level%20of%20health%20facilities%20in%20developed%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20said%20his%20government%20had%20carried%20out%20unprecedented%20expansion%20in%20AIIMS%20and%20medical%20colleges%20as%20well%20as%20critical%20infrastructure%20network%20by%20opening%20more%20than%20one%20lakh%20'Ayushman%20Arogya%20Mandirs'%20in%20villages%2C%20and%20taking%20the%20number%20of%20medical%20colleges%20to%20706%20from%20308-309%20a%20decade%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20MBBS%20and%20medical%20PG%20seats%20have%20increased%20during%20this%20period%20to%20more%20than%20one%20lakh%20and%2070%2C000%2C%20respectively%2C%20from%2050%2C000%20and%2030%2C000%2C%20he%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20priority%20of%20his%20government%20was%20towards%20prevention%20of%20diseases%20by%20increasing%20the%20capacity%20to%20fight%20them%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20focused%20on%20nutrition%2C%20Yoga%2C%20AYUSH%20and%20cleanliness%20so%20that%20diseases%20can%20be%20prevented%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20hospitals%20and%20research%20centres%20for%20Yoga%20and%20naturopathy%20have%20been%20inaugurated%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%20as%20part%20of%20such%20efforts%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20constant%20endeavour%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20ensure%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20middle%20class%20get%20quality%20medical%20treatment%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20has%20hel