y%20the%20BJP%20passes%20through%20sugarcane%20fields%20in%20Budhana%2C%20Muzaffarnagar.%20The%20bikes%20are%20decorated%20with%20flags%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%20while%20a%20song%20plays%20in%20the%20background%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Mazdoor%20kisan%20ke%20haq%20mein%20ye%20alakh%20jagai%20re%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ERLD%20aayi%20re%2C%20RLD%20aayi%20re%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98(This%20awakening%20is%20happening%20in%20support%20of%20labourers%20and%20farmers%2C%20RLD%20%5BRashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%5D%20has%20come%2C%20RLD%20has%20come).%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20sugarcane%20plots%20belong%20to%20Shobhan%20Singh%2C%2080%20who%20has%20seen%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20politics.%20A%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20been%20set%20up%2C%20at%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20fields%2C%20where%20he%20sits%20with%20a%20hookah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20thoughts%2C%20Shobhan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Sahib%20deserved%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20but%20no%20past%20prime%20minister%20thought%20of%20honouring%20him%20in%20this%20manner.%20Now%20it%20is%20natural%20for%20Chaudhary%20Sahib%E2%80%99s%20grandson%20Jayant%20to%20lean%20towards%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20nod%20in%20agreement%2C%20puffing%20on%20their%20hookahs%2C%20wondering%20aloud%20farmer%20Shivam%20Choudhary%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDadda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20do%20you%20think%20that%20Bharat%20Ratna%20alone%20made%20Jayant%20Choudhary%20distance%20himself%20from%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERLD%E2%80%99s%20prospects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERLD%20chief%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20staunch%20opposition%20to%20the%20BJP%20truly%20shocked%20everyone%20by%20parting%20ways%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20and%20switching%20loyalties%20to%20the%20NDA%20within%20hours%20of%20Bharat%20Ratna%20award%20announcement%20for%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20on%20February%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20day%2C%20while%20speaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20a%20turncoat%20Jayant%20said%20aloud%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20been%20in%20the%20opposition%20for%2010%20years%2C%20I%20see%20shades%20of%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20ideology%20in%20the%20present%20government%E2%80%99s%20working%20style.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20towering%20figure%20in%20farmer%20politics%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20had%20devised%20a%20caste%20coalition%20formula%20then%20popularly%20known%20%E2%80%98MAJGAR%E2%80%99%20(Muslim%2C%20Ahir%2C%20Jat%2C%20Gujjar%2C%20and%20Rajput%20communities)%20which%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20his%20success%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-bharat-ratna-chaudhary-charan-singh-politics-meant-the-art-of-possible%5C%22%3EFor%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Ratna%E2%80%99%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Politics%20Meant%20the%20Art%20of%20the%20Possible%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20was%20a%20grassroots%20leader%2C%20representing%20farmers%20of%20all%20castes.%20However%2C%20after%20his%20passing%20away%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20diminished%2C%20narrowing%20down%20to%20primarily%20representing%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20senior%20journalist%20Brijesh%20Shukla.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20downfall%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20its%20tendency%20to%20align%20with%20larger%20parties%20like%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%2C%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20strengthening%20its%20own%20foundation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20even%20the%20Jat%20support%20base%20of%20the%20RLD%20began%20to%20dwindle%20particularly%20on%20account%20of%20the%20divide%20between%20Muslims%20and%20Jats%20essentially%20following%20the%20infamous%202013%20Muzaffarnagar%20riots%20which%20left%20more%20than%2065%20people%20dead%20and%20thousands%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CSDS%20post-poll%20studies%20on%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20garnered%2077%25%20of%20the%20Jat%20votes%2C%20a%20stark%20increase%20from%20the%207%25%20it%20received%20in%20the%202012%20Assembly%20elections.%20In%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20there%20was%20a%20considerable%20anticipation%20as%20an%20ambitious%20grand%20alliance%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20and%20RLD%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Muslims%2C%20Jats%20and%20Dalits%20comprising%20approximately%2060%25%20of%20the%20voting%20population%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20RLD%20harboured%20high%20hopes.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20results%20were%20announced%2C%20it%20sent%20shockwaves%20as%20both%20Ajit%20Singh%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20lost%20their%20seats%20once%20again%2C%20with%20the%20RLD%20failing%20to%20even%20open%20its%20account%20and%20the%20BJP%20took%20away%2091%25%20of%20the%20Jat%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20election%2C%20unfolded%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20massive%20farmer%20protests%20in%20the%20western%20region%20that%20had%20been%20ongoing%20for%20months.%20The%20RLD%20then%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP%20hoped%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20Muslims%20and%20Jats.%20However%2C%20the%20results%20remained%20shocking%20for%20RLD%20which%20failed%20to%20win%20more%20than%208%20of%20the%2033%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijesh%20Shukla%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20RLD%20failed%20to%20secure%20victory%20despite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20grand%20alliance%20in%202019%20or%20amidst%20extensive%20farmer%20protests%20in%202022%2C%20when%20the%20odds%20were%20stacked%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20see%20how%20they%20could%20emerge%20victorious%20in%202024.%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20was%20already%20fighting%20a%20losing%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayant%20Choudhary%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20join%20the%20NDA%20alliance%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20notable%20advantage%20for%20the%20RLD%2C%20signalling%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20party%20securing%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20prospect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20village%20of%20Firozpur%20Bangar%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath%20is%20seen%20engaging%20with%20villagers%20during%20a%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%20session%2C%20where%20he%20acquaints%20them%20with%20various%20beneficiary%20schemes%20initiated%20by%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20launches%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Gram%20Parikrama%20Yatra%20in%20the%20state%2C%20slated%20to%20cover%2050%2C000%20villages%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Following%20the%20%3Cem%3Echaupal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20addressing%20villagers%20in%20a%20rally%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20have%20always%20greeted%20each%20other%20with%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%20Sa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ERam%20Ramji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20With%20the%20divine%20arrival%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20the%20recognition%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20with%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20on%20the%20other%2C%20I%20urge%20our%20farmers%20to%20convey%20their%20felicitations%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20in%20the%20region%2C%20highlighting%20four%20major%20issues%20the%20party%20is%20focusing%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3A%20hindutva%2C%20utilising%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20to%20woo%20Jayant%20and%20farmers%2C%20beneficiary%20schemes%2C%20and%20capitalising%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamshad%20Khan%2C%20psephologist%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20the%C2%A0PEACS%C2%A0news%20service%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CChaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20commands%20immense%20respect%20in%20the%20region.%20By%20awarding%20him%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20accomplish%20two%20objectives%3A%20building%20goodwill%20among%20farmers%20and%20drawing%20RLD%20into%20their%20camp%2C%20thereby%20dealing%20a%20significant%20psychological%20blow%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20and%20SP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradeshs-economy-down-the-rabbit-hole-and-beyond%5C%22%3EUttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Economy%3A%20Down%20the%20Rabbit%20Hole%20and%20Beyond%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%20the%20BJP%20is%20also%20working%20to%20get%20its%20caste%20equation%20right%20in%20the%20region.%20Laxmi%20Kant%20Bajpai%2C%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Meerut%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20Jats%2C%20but%20we%20have%20also%20actively%20connected%20with%20numerically%20smaller%20communities%20in%20the%20region%2C%20such%20as%20Tyagis%2C%20Sainis%2C%20Gujjars%2C%20Lohaars%2C%20Kahaars%2C%20and%20Kanchis.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20various%20beneficiary%20schemes%20have%20significantly%20benefited%20these%20groups%2C%20and%20we%20expect%20even%20stronger%20support%20from%20them%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20BSP%20steadily%20losing%20its%20hold%20over%20its%20Dalit%20base%2C%20all%20political%20rivals%20are%20out%20to%20grab%20whatever%20they%20can%20out%20of%20the%20Dalit%20vote.%20And%20BJP%20appears%20to%20be%20way%20ahead%20of%20others%2C%20having%20already%20secured%20a%20substantial%20portion%20of%20Dalit%20voters%20from%20the%20BSP%2C%20the%20party%20is%20continuing%20its%20efforts%20to%20expand%20its%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172719%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.25.31-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172719%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.25.31-PM.png%20864w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23172719%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-23-at-5.25.31-PM-300x208.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-698557%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20leader%20Asim%20Arun%20during%20a%20campaign%20trail.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40asim_arun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20made%20substantial%20efforts%20toward%20the%20upliftment%20of%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities.%20Not%20only%20have%20our%20welfare%20schemes%20greatly%20benefited%20these%20communities%20but%20the%20BJP%20has%20also%20paid%20homage%20to%20icons%20like%20Baba%20Saheb%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20and%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20instilling%20confidence%20that%20Modi%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20will%20continue%20to%20empower%20every%20downtrodden%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Asim%20Arun%2C%20former%20police%20commissioner%20of%20Kanpur%20and%20now%20minister%20of%20social%20welfare%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%2021%20days%20prior%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20announcement%20to%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20posted%20a%20picture%20on%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%20with