w%20electoral%20strategy%2C%20banking%20on%20the%20support%20from%20Dalit%20voters.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20significant%20shift%20is%20expected%20in%20west%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20among%20the%20Dalit%20voters.%20Recent%20by-polls%20in%20Mainpuri%2C%20Rampur%2C%20and%20Ghosi%20saw%20strong%20support%20from%20the%20scheduled%20caste%20voters%20for%20the%20SP%20and%20this%20trend%20will%20continue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBSP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati%E2%80%99s%20BSP%2C%20once%20a%20formidable%20force%20in%20the%20western%20region%2C%20has%20seen%20a%20decline%20in%20its%20influence.%20The%20factors%20contributing%20to%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20historical%20strength%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20included%20the%20significant%20presence%20of%20Dalits%2C%20particularly%20Jatavs%2C%20a%20sub-caste%20to%20which%20Mayawati%20belongs%2C%20alongside%20support%20from%20Muslims%20who%20viewed%20the%20BSP-Jatav%20combination%20as%20a%20winning%20formula.%20Additionally%2C%20BSP%20had%20an%20array%20of%20influential%20leaders%20and%20a%20motivated%20cadre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20political%20commentator%20Ajmal%20Rahi%2C%20who%20also%20runs%20an%20organisation%20for%20communal%20harmony%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20highlights%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20current%20situation%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BSP%20is%20almost%20finished%20in%20the%20region%3B%20they%20lack%20major%20issues%2C%20their%20cadres%20have%20weakened%2C%20and%20influential%20leaders%20have%20left%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20BSP%20leaders%20see%20Jayant%E2%80%99s%20departure%20from%20the%20SP%20alliance%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20regain%20Muslim%20support%20by%20positioning%20BSP%20as%20the%20main%20alternative%20to%20the%20BJP.%20With%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20Jatav%20base%20remaining%20strong%2C%20the%20alliance%20of%20Jatav%20and%20Muslim%20voters%20could%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%C2%A0refutes%20and%20s