%20T20%20tournament.%20This%20sounds%20very%20odd.%20When%20I%20am%20watching%20the%20BPL%2C%20I%20sometimes%20turn%20off%20the%20TV.%20Some%20players%20are%20not%20even%20of%20the%20%5Brequired%5D%20class.%20I%20have%20a%20big%20issue%20with%20the%20current%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hathurusingha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ICC%20need%20to%20step%20in.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20some%20regulations.%20A%20player%20is%20playing%20one%20tournament%20and%20then%20he%20is%20playing%20another%20tournament.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20circus.%20Players%20will%20talk%20about%20opportunities%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20right.%20People%20will%20lose%20interest.%20I%20have%20lost%20interest%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hathurusingha%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHathurusingha%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20Bangladesh%20cricketers%20are%20not%20getting%20enough%20practice%20in%20key%20sectors%20like%20batting%20in%20the%20Top%203%20and%20bowling%20death%20overs.%20He%20suggested%20that%20there%20should%20be%20another%20tournament%20ahead%20of%20the%20BPL%20to%20help%20in%20the%20development%20of%20local%20cricketers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20have%20a%20tournament%20where%20our%20players%20can%20do%20things%20like%20batting%20in%20the%20top%20three.%20Bangladesh%20bowlers%20bowling%20in%20the%20death.%20Where%20will%20we%20learn%20these%20things%20otherwise%3F%20We%20have%20only%20one%20tournament%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hathurusingha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20suggestion%20is%20that%20we%20have%20another%20tournament%20before%20the%20BPL.%20The%20franchises%20do%20what%20they%20want.%20Some%20of%20the%20best%20players%20are%20not%20playing.%20Then%20how%20do%20you%20expect%20the%20Bangladesh%20team%20to%20be%20up%20with%20the%20other%20teams%3F%20I%20am%20fighting%20a%20steep%20battle%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hathurusingha%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708859880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fq4deavc_s_625x300_25_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbpl-is-like-a-circus-bangladesh-cricket-team-head-coachs-fiery-rant-on-t20-league-5124605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chandika%20Hathurusingha%20said%20that%20the%20country%20does%20not%20have%20a%20proper%20T20%20tournament%20and%20launched%20a%20fiery%20rant%20on%20Bangladesh%20Premier%20League%20(BPL).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BD%20Fadnavis%20Trying%20To%20Divide%20Marathas%26quot%3B%3A%20Quota%20Agitation%20Leader%20Hits%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20Maratha%20quota%20agitation%20leader%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20today%20accused%20the%20BJP%20leader%20of%20hatching%20a%20plot%20to%20deny%20quota%20benefits%20to%20members%20of%20the%20community.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Patil%20today%20threatened%20to%20begin%20a%20march%20to%20Mr%20Fadnavis'%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFadnavis%20has%20taken%20a%20decision%20without%20taking%20(Chief%20Minister%20Eknath)%20Shinde%20in%20the%20loop.%20Everything%20is%20happening%20on%20his%20directions%2C%20he%20is%20running%20the%20state.%20Does%20Fadnavis%20want%20me%20to%20sacrifice%20myself%3F%20I%20wil%20march%20to%20his%20bungalow.%20Stop%20me%20if%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Patil%2C%20who%20hit%20headlines%20for%20his%20hunger%20strike%20in%20demand%20of%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20last%20week%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20provide%20quota%20benefits%20to%20the%20politically-influential%20community%20that%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20new%20law%20is%20not%20in%20line%20with%20their%20demand.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20reservation%20which%20we%20deserve%2C%20give%20reservation%20under%20OBC%20category%20to%20those%20whose%20proof%20of%20being%20Kunbi%20has%20been%20found.%20For%20those%20who%20don't%20have%20proof%2C%20pass%20a%20law%20of%20'Sage%20Soyare'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patil%20said%20after%20the%20Bill%20cleared%20the%20Assembly.%20The%20quota%20agitation%20leader%20is%20demanding%20benefits%20for%20blood%20relations%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Kunbi%20sub-caste%20among%20Marathas.%20The%20Kunbis%20enjoy%20reservation%20within%20the%20OBC%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20agitation%2C%20Mr%20Patil%20had%20demanded%20that%20all%20members%20of%20Maratha%20community%20be%20considered%20Kunbi%20and%20given%20reservations%20under%20the%20OBC%20Quota%2C%20but%20the%20state%20government%20decided%20that%20only%20people%20with%20Nizam-era%20Kunbi%20certificates%20will%20get%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFadnavis%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20rift%20within%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20Attempts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20finish%20big%20communities%20and%20give%20more%20prominence%20to%20smaller%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20said%20he%20is%20not%20affiliated%20to%20any%20political%20party.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20farmer's%20son.%20I%20will%20not%20spare%20Fadnavis.%20Attempts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20Maratha%20community%20and%20defame%20me.%20Fadnavis%20will%20be%20wiped%20off.%20I%20will%20ensure%20that%20relatives%20(of%20Marathas)%20get%20quota%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20brought%20by%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20is%20the%20third%20attempt%20in%20a%20decade%20to%20provide%20reservation%20benefits%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20The%20earlier%20two%20attempts%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20Congress's%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20and%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20were%20struck%20down%20by%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20factor%20behind%20the%20setbacks%20to%20the%20earlier%20laws%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20took%20the%20quantum%20of%20total%20reservation%20past%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20ceiling%20fixed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20warned%20that%20the%20legislation%20may%20not%20eventually%20clear%20the%20judicial%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20said%20it%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20brought%20by%20the%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20government.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20fresh%20bill%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%20State%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20has%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20for%20bringing%20the%20law%20just%20before%20the%20elections.%20%26quot%3BThese%20types%20of%20laws%20were%20brought%20two%20times%2C%20but%20they%20were%20scrapped%20and%20put%20in%20a%20bin%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20In%202019%2C%20they%20did%20for%20the%20winning%20elections%20and%20now%20also%20they%20did%20for%20the%20elections.%20They%20want%20to%20take%20the%20credit%20for%20this.%20This%20will%20not%20work%20because%20it%20is%20done%20only%20for%20the%20election%20to%20get%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20has%20welcomed%20the%20legislation%20but%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20can%20be%20said%26quot%3B%20till%20it%20is%20implemented.%20Taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20his%20estranged%20lieutenant%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20knows%20the%20history%20of%20CM%20(Shinde).%20Therefore%2C%20till%20the%20time%20whatever%20he%20has%20said%20is%20implemented%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708859340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fvtf77ti8_manoj-jarange-patil_625x300_25_February_24.jpg%22%2C