0had%20forgotten%20them.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20heart-wrenching%20waking%20up%20to%20such%20allegations%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Jahan%20wrote.%C2%A0She%20said%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20come%20together%20%26quot%3Bto%20help%20create%20peace%20and%20not%20commotion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20heart%20wrenching%20waking%20up%20to%20such%20allegations.%20As%20a%20woman%2C%20as%20a%20public%20representative%20I%20have%20always%20followed%20my%20parties%20guidelines%20and%20served%20the%20people.%20With%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20incident%20raging%2C%20Our%20Hon%20CM%20has%20already%20send%20Help..%20and%20necessary%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20for%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKrqOeSvWU0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKrqOeSvWU0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nussrat%20Jahan%20(%40nusratchirps)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnusratchirps%2Fstatus%2F1761644455835423187%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20woman%2C%20as%20a%20public%20representative%2C%20I%20have%20always%20followed%20my%20parties%20guidelines%20and%20served%20the%20people.%20With%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20incident%20raging%2C%20Our%20Hon%20CM%20has%20already%20send%20Help..%20and%20necessary%20steps%20are%20being%20taken%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20people.%20We%20are%20not%20above%20the%20law..%20thus%20abiding%20by%20it%20and%20supporting%20the%20administration%20is%20what%20one%20needs%20to%20do.%20I%20have%20genuinely%20served%20the%20people%20in%20my%20constituency%2C%20in%20times%20of%20joy%2C%20in%20times%20of%20trouble..%20I%20act%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20guidelines%20of%20my%20party..%20and%20I%20believe%20we%20must%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20state%20govt%20and%20administration%2Cwhat%20is%20wrong%20shall%20always%20be%20condemned.%20We%20must%20refrain%20from%20targeting%20each%20other%20and%20come%20together%20to%20help%20create%20peace%20and%20not%20commotion.%20People's%20security%20and%20welfare%20is%20our%20top%20priority.%20Rest%20who%20says%20what%20about%20whom%20does%20not%20matter.%20Like%20I%20said%20before.%20I'd%20repeat%20again%20%26quot%3BSTOP%20POLITICISING%26quot%3B%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20she%20shared%20quoted%20Sandeshkhali%20residents%20as%20saying%20that%20Ms%20Jahan%20did%20not%20visit%20the%20island%20even%20once%20after%20being%20elected.%20The%20only%20time%20she%20was%20there%20was%20during%20the%20poll%20campaign%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20campaign%20vehicle%20in%20which%20she%20had%20toured%20the%20island%20then%20belonged%20to%20local%20Trinamool%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20massive%20row%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20quotes%20local%20women%20as%20saying%20that%20even%20though%20the%20MP%20doesn't%20come%20visiting%2C%20residents%20of%20the%20island%20travel%2040%20km%20or%20more%20to%20watch%20her%20movies%20in%20cinema%20halls.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20prayed%20for%20her%20visit%20to%20the%20island.%20She%20had%20given%20us%20faith%2C%20so%20we%20waited%20for%20her%2C%20but%20she%20did%20not%20keep%20her%20word%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20quoted%20a%20woman%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMain%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20local%20MP%20over%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20situation.%20Shortly%20after%20photos%20of%20her%20Valentine's%20Day%20photoshoot%20with%20actor%20and%20partner%20Yash%20Dasgupta%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20taken%20a%20%26quot%3Bpriorities%20matter%26quot%3B%20swipe.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20women%20are%20protesting%20for%20their%20respect.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20TMC%20MP%20of%20Basirhat%20is%20celebrating%20Valentine's%20Day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bengal%20BJP%20had%20s