20cases%20against%20him%20under%20the%20UAPA%20and%20for%20anti-national%20activities%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20attending%20and%20organising%20SIMI's%20meetings%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Kerala%20and%20was%20declared%20a%20fugitive%20by%20a%20Delhi%20court%20in%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20team%20looking%20for%20him%20for%20the%20past%20four%20years%20received%20information%20that%20Shaikh%20changed%20his%20identity%20and%20was%20now%20going%20as%20Mohammad%20Hanif.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20working%20as%20a%20teacher%20at%20an%20Urdu%20medium%20municipal%20school%20in%20Bhusawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20this%20information%2C%20the%20police%20laid%20a%20trap%20on%20February%2022%20and%20caught%20him%20from%20Bhusawal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20IS%20HANIF%20SHAIKH%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHanif%20Shaikh%20earned%20his%20diploma%20from%20Marul%20Jalgaon%20in%201997.%20He%20joined%20SIMI%20the%20same%20year%20and%20became%20an%20%26quot%3BAnsar%20(full-time%20worker)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20highly%20radicalized%20after%20coming%20in%20contact%20with%20SIMI%20workers.%20He%20began%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20group's%20weekly%20programmes%20and%20started%20radicalising%20young%20Muslims%20to%20join%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImpressed%20by%20his%20enthusiasm%2C%20the%20then%20SIMI%20chief%20Sahid%20Badar%20made%20Shaikh%20the%20editor%20of%20the%20Urdu%20edition%20of%20'Islamic%20Movement'%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20magazine's%20editor%2C%20Shaikh%20wrote%20several%20inflammatory%20articles%2C%20wrongly%2C%20highlighting%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20against%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20he%20was%20allotted%20a%20room%20at%20the%20SIMI%20Headquarters%20in%20Delhi's%20Zakir%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20close%20relationships%20with%20Safdar%20Hussain%20Nagori%2C%20Abdus%20Shubhan%20Qureshi%20alias%20Tauqeer%2C%20Noman%20Badar%2C%20Shahnaz%20Hussain%2C%20Saif%20Nachain%2C%20and%20Mohammad%20-%20all%20members%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20police%20raid%20in%202001%2C%20Hanif%20Shaikh%20managed%20to%20escape%20with%20a%20few%20others%20and%20went%20underground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20kept%20changing%20his%20location%20to%20evade%20arrest%20and%20finally%20made%20his%20way%20to%20Bhusawal%20from%20Jalgaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20admitted%20to%20visiting%20many%20places%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Gujarat%20to%20motivate%20people%20to%20join%20SIMI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20ban%20on%20SIMI%2C%20most%20of%20the%20active%20members%20became%20scattered.%20Some%20have%20independently%20continued%20their%20terrorist%20activities%20and%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20several%20blasts%20and%20other%20anti-national%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20time%2C%20senior%20members%20of%20%26quot%3BWahdat-e-Islam%26quot%3B%20started%20new%20organisations.%20Most%20of%20the%20members%20of%20this%20organisation%20are%20from%20SIMI.%20The%20basic%20agenda%20is%20to%20unite%20young%20Muslims%20and%20propagate%20the%20doctrine%20of%20radical%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20is%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Wahdat-e-Islam%20think%20tank%20and%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20other%20neighbouring%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20involved%20in%20collecting%20money%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20donations%20to%20support%20and%20fund%20the%20agenda%20of%20SIMI%20and%20Wahdat-e-Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20five%20siblings%20-%20three%20brothers%20and%20two%20sisters%2C%20a%20wife%2C%20and%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708851600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F82qgd47o_hanif-shaikh-simi_625x300_25_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F