id%20to%20drive%20away%20evil%20spirits%20and%20where%20participants%20pray%20for%20happiness.%20Despite%20its%20name%2C%20those%20taking%20part%20are%20not%20naked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20women%20wore%20%26quot%3BHappi%20Coats%26quot%3B%20(robes%20that%20reach%20to%20the%20hips)%20and%20shorts%20that%20are%20typically%20worn%20at%20Japanese%20festivals%2C%20although%20men%20just%20wore%20loincloths%20similar%20to%20those%20worn%20by%20sumo%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20heard%20that%20women%20could%20participate%20so%20I%20definitely%20wanted%20to%20take%20part%20to%20help%20bring%20excitement%20to%20this%20town%20and%20festival%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2059-year-old%20civil%20servant%20Emi%20Tachibana%2C%20one%20of%20the%20participants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaruhito%20Tsunoda%2C%20a%20priest%20at%20the%20shrine%2C%20said%20there%20had%20never%20been%20a%20ban%20on%20women%20participating%2C%20and%20some%20had%20even%20made%20small%20offerings%20as%20individuals%20before.%20However%2C%20when%20a%20women's%20group%20inquired%20last%20year%20if%20they%20could%20join%2C%20saying%20'yes'%20was%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20for%20there%20to%20be%20a%20fun%20festival%20for%20everyone.%20I%20think%20God%20would%20be%20happiest%20about%20that%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20did%20not%20join%20the%20festival's%20main%20event%20where%20a%20large%20group%20of%20men%20clash%20together%20to%20drive%20away%20evil%20spirits.%20Tsunoda%20said%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20open%20up%20that%20part%20of%20the%20festival%20to%20women%20due%20to%20the%20physical%20aspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20government%20last%20year%20said%20it%20would%20push%20to%20improve%20women's%20participation%20in%20society%20after%20an%20annual%20report%20showed%20the%20country%20was%20struggling%20to%20narrow%20the%20gender%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20repo