0when%20we%20got%20out%2C%20I%20found%20Hemil%20dead.%20I%20was%20the%20one%20who%20put%20his%20body%20in%20the%20truck%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgujarati-security-helper-in-russian-army-killed-in-ukrainian-air-strike%2Farticle67882488.ece%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20photograph%20of%20Mangukiya%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20showing%20injuries%20and%20blood-soaked%20clothes%2C%20was%20shared%20by%20another%20Indian%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20all%2C%20there%20were%20four%20Indians%20including%20Hemil%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20group%20that%20came%20under%20attack%20on%20February%2021.%20Hemil%20was%20very%20close%20to%20the%20Russian%20military%20commander%20and%20they%20trusted%20him.%20They%20did%20not%20make%20him%20do%20menial%20work.%20The%20air%20strike%20happened%20when%20the%20trench%20was%20being%20dug%20up.%20A%20Nepalese%20was%20also%20among%20those%20killed%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20Indian%20worker%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20email%20sent%20on%20behalf%20of%20Mangukiya%E2%80%99s%20father%20to%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20on%20February%202%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20arrange%20for%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20return%20citing%20the%20risk%20to%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fgovt-in-talks-with-russian-authorities-for-early-discharge-of-indians-forced-to-fight-in-russia%5C%22%3Eapproached%20Russian%20authorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20discharge%E2%80%9D%20of%20Indians%20working%20with%20the%20Russian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20had%20come%20forward%20alleging%20mistreatment%20said%20that%20their%20pleas%20for%20help%20from%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%20had%20gone%20unheard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%