%20her%20house%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20passing%20car%20honked%20many%20times%20but%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20move.%20The%20neighbour%20who%20noticed%20this%20immediately%20told%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20Rajinder%20Kaur%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20your%20daughter%20can%20hear.%20Take%20her%20to%20the%20doctor!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajinder%20hurriedly%20took%20her%20two-and-a-half-year-old%20daughter%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20where%20the%20doctor%20diagnosed%20her%20with%20severe%20hearing%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20many%20hospitals%20after%20that%2C%20including%20AIIMS.%20Everyone%20gave%20the%20same%20diagnosis.%20They%20said%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20cochlear%20implant%2C%20which%20would%20cost%20almost%20Rs%206%20to%207%20lakh.%20My%20husband%20is%20an%20auto%20driver%20and%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20fathom%20how%20to%20cough%20up%20such%20a%20big%20amount%20of%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajinder%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20passed%20as%20the%20couple%20visited%20various%20hospitals%20and%20explored%20different%20options.%20In%202014%2C%20when%20the%20child%20was%20five%20years%20old%2C%20they%20were%20introduced%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20which%20offered%20assistance.%20With%20their%20financial%20support%2C%20Sukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20that%20year%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20a%20mainstream%20school%20just%20like%20any%20other%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20can%20now%20speak%20well%20and%20is%20a%20good%20student.%20She%20also%20paints%20very%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Rajinder%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20yearning%20to%20hear%20her%20speak.%20Now%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20of%20it!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20school%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fimage-1708783652-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESukhjot%20received%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20and%20is%20now%20flourishing%20in%20school.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20intervention%20has%20supported%20the%20surgeries%20and%20rehabilitation%20of%20over%20900%20children%20across%2014%20hospitals%20in%20seven%20states%2C%20from%20its%20start%20in%20December%202013%20to%20date.%20Dr%20Ravi%20Bhatia%2C%20an%20ENT%20surgeon%20at%20Sarvodaya%20Hospital%20%E2%80%94%20a%20partner%20of%20THF%20%E2%80%94%20explains%20that%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20aids%20children%20with%20severe%20hearing%20loss%20in%20listening%2C%20understanding%2C%20and%20beginning%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cochlear%20implant%20is%20an%20electronic%20device%20which%20is%20implanted%20through%20surgery%20into%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20ear.%20It%20bypasses%20the%20damaged%20hair%20cells%20of%20the%20inner%20ear%20or%20cochlea%20to%20provide%20sound%20signals%20to%20the%20brain%20by%20stimulating%20the%20inner%20ear%2C%20which%20helps%20the%20child%20to%20start%20hearing.%20There%20is%20an%20internal%20and%20external%20device%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implant%20comprises%20an%20external%20component%20placed%20behind%20the%20ear%20and%20a%20second%20component%20surgically%20implanted%20under%20the%20skin.%20This%20surgery%20can%20be%20performed%20as%20early%20as%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20of%20age%20and%20ideally%20should%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20reaches%20three%20years%20old%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20access%20to%20schooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20newborn%20hearing%20screening%2C%20the%20doctors%20can%20assess%20if%20the%20baby%20has%20any%20hearing%20loss.%20Through%20a%20battery%20of%20tests%20and%20follow-ups%2C%20by%20the%20time%20the%20child%20is%20three%20to%20four%20months%20old%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20if%20the%20baby%20needs%20a%20cochlear%20implant%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20baby%20reaches%20eight%20months%20old%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20for%20the%20surgery%2C%20which%20typically%20lasts%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20surgery%20alone%20addresses%20only%2020%20percent%20of%20the%20problem.%20What%E2%80%99s%20equally%20important%20is%20the%20post-surgery%20Auditory%20Verbal%20Therapy%20(AVT)%2C%20which%20spans%20two%20years%20and%20requires%20parental%20involvement%20to%20ensure%20the%20child%20develops%20spoken%20language%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHF%20states%20that%20each%20cochlear%20implant%20procedure%20with%20the%20device%2C%20surgery%20and%20rehabilitation%20costs%20about%20Rs%208-9%20lakh%20per%20ear.%20THF%20also%20provides%20support%20for%20this%20therapy%20and%20ensures%20that%20parents%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20have%20access%20to%20therapists%20and%20can%20continue%20the%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20warning%20signs%20of%20hearing%20loss%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-5%20age%20group%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-16-1708783874-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECochlear%20implant%20surgery%20is%20most%20effective%20when%20done%20in%20the%200-3%20age%20group%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20in%20Sukhjot%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20many%20parents%20come%20to%20doctors%20late%2C%20says%20Dr%20Bhatia.%20This%20lack%20of%20awareness%20causes%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20surgery%2C%20affecting%20outcomes.%20An%20internal%20study%20conducted%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20revealed%20that%20hearing%20outcomes%20among%20children%20who%20received%20implants%20between%20the%20ages%20of%20zero%20and%20three%20were%20two%20and%20a%20half%20times%20improved%20compared%20to%20those%20implanted%20at%20ages%20four%20and%20older.%20Hence%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20identify%20and%20undergo%20implantation%20before%20the%20age%20of%20three%20for%20a%20favourable%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20parents%20are%20in%20denial%20about%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328341%2Fyunikee-empowers-deaf-persons-accessing-hearing-solutions-govt-jobs-skills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20loss%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20India.%20Elders%20also%20support%20their%20beliefs%20saying%20that%20even%20we%20spoke%20late.%20When%20a%20child%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20listen%20to%20sounds%20or%20react%20to%20sounds%2C%20parents%20must%20raise%20a%20red%20flag.%20Go%20to%20a%20doctor%20and%20get%20your%20child%20checked%20if%20you%20notice%20anything%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Bhatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20grows%20its%20commitment%20to%20supporting%20several%20life-changing%20medical%20interventions%20for%20children%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20under%20its%20larger%20umbrella%20of%20Hans%20Paediatric%20Care%2C%20support%20for%20children%20who%20need%20cochlear%20implant%20surgeries%20remains%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHF%20works%20closely%20with%20its%20hospital%20partners%20for%20these%20surgeries.%20Doctors%20from%20the%20partner%20hospitals%20and%20their%20networks%20identify%20children%20who%20need%20support%20and%20connect%20them%20with%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20programme.%20THF%20ensures%20that%20the%20family%20is%20prepared%20to%20commit%20to%20post-surgery%20therapy%20and%20maintain%20the%20device%20properly.%20Dr%20Bhatia%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20periodic%20battery%20replacements%20and%20regular%20cleaning%20of%20the%20device.%20Additionally%2C%20patients%20should%20take%20precautions%20to%20avoid%20ear%20injuries%20and%20promptly%20seek%20medical%20attention%20in%20case%20of%20infections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20a%20decade%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20programme%2C%20the%20Foundation%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20success%20of%20a%20cochlear%20implant%20is%20based%20on%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors.%20The%20cause%20and%20type%20of%20hearing%20impairment%20have%20an%20effect%2C%20but%20so%20does%20the%20age%20of%20the%20child%2C%20time%20elapsed%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20hearing%20loss%2C%20active%20implant%20use%2C%20and%20also%20family%20support%20which%20affects%20the%20quality%20of%20speech%20and%20educational%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Bhatia%20urges%20parents%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20ignore%20any%20warning%20signs%20or%20doubts.%20Just%20go%20and%20consult%20a%20doctor.%20Cochlear%20implants%20are%20nothing%20to%20be%20wary%20of%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20a%20well%20established%20technology%20and%20can%20change%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20life%20for%20the%20better%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20The%20Hans%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708836709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20spotting%20hearing%20loss%20in%20children%20early%20on%20and%20offering%20life-changing%20surgery%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20has%20helped%20over%20900%20children%20with%20its%20Cochlear%20Implant%20Programme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343108%2Fthe-hans-foundation-cochlear-implant-program-for-children-with-hearing-loss-deaf-speech-hospital-surgery%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Not%20giving%20up%20the%20fight'%3A%20Nikki%20Haley%20despite%20Trump's%20projected%20win%20in%20South%20Carolina%20primary%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708834282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107979549%2Cimgsize-819734.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnikki-haley-vows-to-continue-fight-despite-trumps-win-in-south-carolina-primary%2Farticleshow%2F107979111.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107979111.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFormer%20South%20Carolina%20Governor%20Nikki%20Haley%20will%20continue%20running%20for%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20nominee.%20She%20believes%20Trump%20can't%20defeat%20Biden%20in%20a%20rematch%20election.%20Haley%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20the%20voters%20of%20South%20Carolina%20and%20shared%20a%20special%20moment%20voting%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20a%20former%20female%20judge%20in%20the%20United%20States.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnikki-haley-vows-to-continue-fight-despite-trumps-win-in-south-carolina-primary%2Farticleshow%2F107979111.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnikki-haley-vows-to-continue-fight-despite-trumps-win-in-south-carolina-primary%2Famp_articleshow%2F107979111.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnikki-haley-vows-to-continue-fight-despite-trumps-win-in-south-carolina-primary%2Famp_articleshow%2F107979111.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Why%20Can%E2%80%99t%20SC%20Take%20Note%20of%20Misuse%20of%20UAPA%20and%20PMLA%3F%E2%80%99%3A%20Legal%20Experts%20on%20Misuse%20of%20Laws%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F16195602%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-16-at-7.55.39-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Senior%20advocate%20Mihir%20Desai%20has%20questioned%20why%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20refused%20to%20take%20note%20of%20the%20misuse%20of%20laws%20such%20as%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20while%20addressing%20a%20seminar%20on%20the%20recent%20trends%20in%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20administration%2C%20management%20and%20cases%20concerning%20civil%20liberties%20and%20political%20rights%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seminar%20was%20held%20on%20Saturday%20(February%2024)%20and%20was%20organised%20by%20the%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20crush%20dissent%2C%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20ways%20which%20the%20government%20has%20found%20is%20to%20use%20UAPA%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Desai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20people%20are%20being%20put%20in%2C%20not%20because%20of%20any%20incident%20which%20has%20happened%2C%20but%20over%20suspicion.%20And%20what%20is%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20response%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20referring%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20taking%20note%20of%20the%20nexus%20between%20money%20and%20politics%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%2C%20Desai%20asked%20why%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20judicial%20note%20of%20misuse%20of%20PMLA%20and%20UAPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20can%E2%80%99t%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20take%20judicial%20notice%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20UAPA%20is%20being%20misused%3F%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20it%20take%20judicial%20notice%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20PMLA%20is%20being%20regularly%20used%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20have%20to%20always%20bow%20down%20to%20what%20the%20solicitor%20general%20says%20even%20though%20it%20is%20not%20a%20constitutional%20post.%20Anytime%20someone%20raises%20the%20issue%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20he%20jumps%20up%20and%20says%20%E2%80%98we%20know%20on%20behalf%20of%20whom%20you%20are%20acting%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20neighbouring%20country%E2%80%99.%20But%20the%20judges%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20gumption%20to%20ask%20him%20to%20shut%20up%20and%20sit%20down.%20In%20the%20US%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20known%20as%20the%20chief%20justice%E2%80%99s%20court.%20In%20India%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20should%20be%20known%20as%20Tushar%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20court.%20That%20is%20the%20situation%20we%20have%20come%20to.%20And%20nobody%20has%20the%20guts%20to%20call%20him%20out%20and%20say%20enough%20is%20enough.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesai%20was%20speaking%20at%20the%20second%20session%20of%20the%20seminar%20%E2%80%98The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20recent%20trend%20on%20cases%20involving%20Civil%20Liberties%20and%20Political%20Rights%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20civil%20liberties%20and%20political%20rights%20has%20become%20critical%20amidst%20a%20surge%20in%20arrests%20of%20activists%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20politicians%20by%20central%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Authority%20on%20questionable%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speakers%20included%20Justices%20A.K.%20Patnaik%20and%20Indira%20Banerjee%2C%20former%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3B%20professor%20Mohan%20Gopal%2C%20former%20director%2C%20National%20Judicial%20Academy%3B%20senior%20advocates%20Trideep%20Pais%2C%20Kapil%20Sibal%3B%20and%20Warisha%20Farasat%2C%20advocate%2C%20Delhi%20high%20court%20and%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPais%20in%20his%20speech%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20modus%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20FIRs%20that%20are%20coming%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20new%20modus%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20FIRs%20we%20deal%20with%20nowadays.%20There%20are%20certain%20persons%20who%20speak%20in%20the%20parliament%20about%20something%20they%20are%20outraged%20by%20and%20that%20is%20tweeted%20by%20some%20other%20important%20person%20and%20then%20carried%20out%20by%20new%20channels%20for%203-4%20days%2C%20by%20the%20fourth%20or%20fifth%20day%20it%20becomes%20an%20FIR.%20This%20modus%20has%20come%20to%20stay.%20This%20is%20the%20way%20a%20UAPA%20case%20comes%20to%20proceed%2C%20this%20is%20the%20pattern%20which%20I%20have%20gathered%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Pais%20did%20not%20take%20any%20names%2C%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-report%5C%22%3Emonsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecited%20a%20report%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20including%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20news%20organisation%20NewsClick%20had%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%E2%80%9D%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20owner%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20has%20since%20been%20charged%20with%20UAPA%20and%20is%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPais%20said%20those%20charged%20under%20UAPA%20find%20it%20more%20difficult%20to%20get%20bail%20than%20in%20PMLA%20or%20NDPS%20(Narcotics%20Drugs%20and%20Psychotropic%20Substances%20Act%20)%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Gopal%20in%20his%20speech%20said%20at%20present%20the%20judgements%20on%20civil%20liberties%20and%20political%20rights%20need%20to%20be%20understood%20in%20the%20context%20of%20two%20types%20of%20judgements%20that%20are%20being%20given%20now-constitutionalist%20which%20is%20ingrained%20in%20the%20Constitution%20and%20theocratic%20judgements%20where%20the%20comes%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20we%20have%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20constitution%20into%20religion%20to%20give%20judgements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Ayodhya%20title%20dispute%20judgement%20and%20the%20hijab%20judgement%2C%20Gopal%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20polity%20where%20religion%20has%20no%20space%2C%20idols%20are%20being%20brought%20in%20through%20these%20theocratic%20judgements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImagine%20an%20edifice%20structure%20%E2%80%93%20our%20polity%20where%20religion%20has%20no%20space%20and%20most%20sacred%20foundation%20is%20the%20belief%20that%20all%20power%20comes%20from%20the%20people%2C%20and%20into%20that%20space%20you%20are%20bringing%20in%20idols%2C%20through%20these%20idols%20through%20these%20theocratic%20judgements.%20It%20may%20take%20half%20a%20century%20to%20change%2C%20bring%20down%20these%20structures%20and%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20theological%20state%20and%20that%20construction%20is%20going%20on%20presently%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarasat%20said%20that%20bail%20jurisprudence%20and%20how%20investigations%20are%20taking%20place%20especially%20in%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20cases%2C%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20cases%20or%20in%20Newsclick%20case%20shows%20that%20police%20are%20not%20acting%20in%20good%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20moment%20a%20client%20booked%20under%20UAPA%20walks%20in%20to%20my%20office%2C%20we%20advise%20that%20we%20will%20move%20for%20bail%20after%206%20months%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20were%20are%20advising%20now.%20We%20are%20in%20a%20very%20serious%20situation.%20We%20say%20let%E2%80%99s%20not%20do%20anything%20until%20chargesheet%20is%20filed.%20We%20are%20starting%20at%20a%20point%20of%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%2C%20she%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clazy%20line%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20the%20owner%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20we%20look%20at%20terror%20cases%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20does%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20be%20fair.%20The%20jurisprudence%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20until%20recently%20was%20about%20liberty%20and%20was%20leaning%20towards%20giving%20people%20their%20liberty%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20offence%20was.%20I%20think%20those%20days%20are%20now%20gone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibal%20in%20his%20speech%20said%20that%20it%20is%20time%20to%20question%20the%20genesis%20of%20this%20law%20of%20CRPC%20and%20IPC%20which%20were%20derived%20from%20British%20colonial%20laws%20which%20were%20used%20to%20quell%20dissent%20simply%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20suspicion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20British%20had%20this%20provision%20that%20you%20can%20arrest%20anybody%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20suspicion-why%20did%20they%20do%20it%3F%20Because%20they%20wanted%20to%20quell%20dissent%20and%20stop%20anybody%20to%20talk%20against%20the%20British%20government.%20How%20does%20this%20provision%20pass%20the%20test%20of%20constitutionality%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20suspect%20anybody.%20What%20is%20the%20basis%3F%20That%20is%20subjective.%20It%20cannot%20be%20objective.%20There%20is%20no%20procedure%20to%20make%20it%20objective%20in%20CRPC.%20I%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20genesis%20of%20criminal%20procedure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibal%20said%20in%20PMLA%20and%20ED%20cases%2C%20arrests%20are%20made%20under%20suspicion%20and%20reasons%20for%20summons%20and%20offences%20are%20not%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHave%20I%20no%20right%20to%20know%3F%20I%20am%20not%20talking%20about%20cases%20where%20there%20is%20a%20murder%20there%20are%20eyewitnesses.%20In%20these%20so%20called%20economic%20offences%20and%20offences%20against%20the%20state%20as%20in%20UAPA%20and%20PMLA%20which%20have%20draconian%20provisions%20which%20according%20to%20me%20are%20entirely%20unconstitutional.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patnaik%20in%20his%20remarks%20said%20that%20the%20most%20important%20qualification%20of%20a%20judge%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccommitment%20to%20civil%20liberties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJudges%20should%20be%20sensitive.%20The%20most%20important%20qualification%20of%20a%20judge%20is%20the%20commitment%20to%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20civil%20liberties%20of%20the%20individuals.%20Second%2C%20you%20must%20have%20a%20very%20independent%20bar%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20for%20the%20executive%20but%20also%20from%20the%20judges.%20Flattery%20of%20a%20judge%20has%20to%20be%20avoided%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20judges%20should%20also%20read%2C%20and%20added%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cimproved%20judgements%20after%20reading.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708834274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F16195602%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-16-at-7.55.39-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-cant-sc-take-note-of-misuse-of-uapa-and-pmla-legal-experts-on-misuse-of-laws%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20remarks%20at%20a%20seminar%20organised%20by%20the%20Campaign%20for%20Judicial%20Accountability%20and%20Reforms%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Wire%20and%20LiveLaw%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Mihir%20Desai%20questioned%20why%20the%20apex%20court%20was%20not%20taking%20note%20like%20it%20had%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwhy-cant-sc-take-note-of-misuse-of-uapa-and-pmla-legal-experts-on-misuse-of-laws%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oppenheimer%20dominates%20SAG%20Awards%20ahead%20of%20Oscars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708833919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%