2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20just%20over%20four%20months%20in%20Gaza%20there%20have%20been%20more%20children%2C%20more%20journalists%20more%20medical%20personnel%20and%20more%20UN%20staff%20killed%20than%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20during%20a%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lazzarini%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20president%20of%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20Dennis%20Francis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELazzarini%20shared%20the%20full%20text%20of%20his%20letter%20in%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20just%20over%20four%20months%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGaza%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20have%20been%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fchildren%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20journalists%2C%20more%20medical%20personnel%2C%20and%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UN%3C%2Fa%3E%20staff%20killed%20than%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20during%20a%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20with%20profound%20regret%20that%20I%20must%20now%20inform%20you%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reached%20a%20breaking%20point%2C%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJbQVk72avu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJbQVk72avu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%20(%40UNLazzarini)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNLazzarini%2Fstatus%2F1760764594644013287%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20allegations%20labelled%20by%20Israel%20in%20January%20against%2012%20UNRWA%20staffers%20accusing%20them%20of%20involvement%20in%20the%20horrific%20October%207%20terror%20attack%2C%20the%20UNRWA%20chief%20said%20%E2%80%9Cto%20date%2C%20no%20evidence%20has%20been%20shared%20by%20Israel%20with%20UNRWA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20resulting%20suspension%20of%20aid%20by%2016%20donor%20countries%20totalling%20%24450%20million%20implies%20that%20without%20new%20funding%20the%20UNRWA%20operations%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20will%20be%20severely%20compromised%20from%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnetanyahu-presents-proposal-for-post-war-gaza%5C%22%3ENetanyahu%20Presents%20Proposal%20for%20Post-War%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisrupt%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20operations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELazzarini%20underlined%20that%20there%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Ca%20concerted%20effort%20by%20some%20Israeli%20officials%20to%20deceptively%20conflate%20UNRWA%20with%20Hamas%2C%20to%20disrupt%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20operations%20and%20to%20call%20for%20the%20dismantling%20of%20the%20agency%E2%80%9D%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20fear%20we%20are%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20monumental%20disaster%20with%20grave%20implications%20for%20regional%20peace%2C%20security%20and%20human%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELazzarini%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20was%20widely%20acknowledged%20that%20UNRWA%20is%20vital%20to%20the%20rights%20and%20security%20of%20both%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%20as%20it%20provides%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstabilising%20role%E2%80%9D%20as%20well%20as%20lifesaving%20humanitarian%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependent%20review%20group%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Secretary%20General%20appointed%20an%20independent%20review%20group%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146207%5C%22%3Eearly%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20Israeli%20allegations%20that%2012%20UNRWA%20employees%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20Hamas-led%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20led%20by%20former%20French%20minister%C2%A0Catherine%20Colonna%20aims%20to%20meet%20Palestinian%20officials%20and%20may%20request%20a%20visit%20to%20Gaza.%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20is%20to%20deliver%20a%20report%20that%20is%20rigorous%20and%20evidence%20based%E2%80%A6and%20to%20do%20our%20best%20so%20we%20can%20help%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%20deliver%20under%20the%20mandate%20given%20%5Bto%20it%5D%20by%20the%20General%20Assembly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Colonna%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146857%5C%22%3EUN%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20began%20its%20work%20on%20February%2013%20and%20expects%20to%20have%20an%20interim%20report%20by%20late%20March.%20Further%2C%20Colonna%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Esaid%20the%20group%20intends%20to%20issue%20recommendations%20in%20its%20final%20report%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20on%20April%2020%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EUN%20News.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemand%20for%20change%20in%20UNRWA%E2%80%99s%20funding%20structure%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELazzarini%20suggested%20that%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20%E2%80%9Cnow%20faces%20a%20fundamental%20decision%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20either%20allow%20UNRWA%20to%20be%20swept%20aside%20without%20political%20consultation%20and%20agreement%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20or%20chose%20to%20make%20a%20moment%20of%20crisis%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccatalyst%20for%20peace%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20case%20he%20urged%20the%20General%20Assembly%20to%20provide%20the%20political%20support%20necessary%20to%20sustain%20UNRWA%