f%20Odisha.%20I%20also%20made%20a%20few%20mistakes%20in%20preparing%20the%20pond%2C%20and%20also%20while%20giving%20supplements%2C%20checking%20the%20pH%20and%20ammonia%20levels%2C%20and%20performing%20surgeries%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334671%2Fmaharashtra-farmers-oyster-pearl-cultivation-battle-drought-suicide-earn-income%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWhen%2520Droughts%2520Led%2520to%2520Losses%252C%2520Oyster%2520Pearl%2520Farming%2520Helped%2520Marathwada%2Cpearl%2520farming%2520to%2520reap%2520profits.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextract%20pearls%20from%20the%20oysters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEarning%20thrice%20the%20inputs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20Vinod%20says%20the%20success%20rate%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20is%20between%2070%20and%2080%20percent.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-3-1708608002-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342925%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECurrently%2C%20Vinod%20says%20the%20success%20rate%20of%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20is%20between%2070%20and%2080%20percent.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20rectified%20these%20mistakes%20in%20the%20second%20batch.%20He%20bought%20another%201%2C000%20oysters%20and%20released%20them%20in%20the%20pond.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20time%2C%20I%20regularly%20checked%20the%20pH%20and%20the%20temperature%20in%20the%20pond.%20Ideally%2C%20the%20pH%20should%20be%207.5%20%5Bbasic%5D%20and%20the%20temperature%20should%20be%20maintained%20between%2025%20and%2030%20degrees.%20During%20summer%2C%20the%20temperature%20shoots%20to%2050%20degrees%20in%20our%20region.%20To%20maintain%20an%20ideal%20temperature%2C%20I%20installed%20a%20green%20shade%20and%20kept%20rotating%20water%20for%203-4%20hours%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20had%20hoped%2C%20the%20success%20rate%20this%20time%20was%2070%20percent.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20this%2C%20I%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20and%20recovered%20the%20investment%20amounts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Vinod%20used%20the%20profits%20to%20expand%20pearl%20farming%20in%20four%20ponds%20spread%20over%20an%20area%20of%20two%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B1.25%20acre%5D.%20In%20the%20last%20batch%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20extract%2010%2C000%20pearls.%20Priced%20at%20Rs%20500%20each%20pearl%2C%20he%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20was%20thrice%20the%20investment%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Many%20officers%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20and%20universities%20often%20visit%20Vinod's%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FPearl-farming-1708608030-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342926%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMany%20officers%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20and%20universities%20often%20visit%20Vinod%E2%80%99s%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20success%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20easy.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20I%20had%20failed%20miserably%2C%20my%20family%20doubted%20my%20capabilities%20and%20I%20had%20to%20face%20negative%20comments%20as%20I%20had%20forcefully%20established%20a%20pond%20inside%20our%20home%20and%20exhausted%20a%20huge%20sum.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20setback.%20I%20focused%20on%20using%20this%20failure%20as%20my%20motivation%20and%20to%20prove%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEventually%2C%20many%20officers%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20and%20universities%20started%20visiting%20my%20farm%20and%20I%20was%20being%20called%20at%20agritech%20fairs%20across%20the%20state.%20I%20have%20received%20recognition%20from%20former%20chief%20ministers%20and%20an%20appreciation%20letter%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20This%20has%20given%20me%20immense%20motivation%20to%20continue%20the%20work%20at%20this%20age.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20have%20managed%20to%20earn%20an%20identity%20by%20doing%20something%20unique%20sitting%20in%20my%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2045-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20informs%20that%20he%20wishes%20to%20establish%20a%20training%20institute%20for%20farmers%20interested%20in%20learning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F89574%2Fsanjay-gandate-pearl-farmer-gadchiroli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20so%20only%20when%20I%20get%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20authorisation.%20A%20farmer%20needs%20loans%20when%20starting%20something%20new.%20For%20this%2C%20they%20need%20to%20show%20certification.%20I%20lack%20that%20authority.%20Not%20everyone%20can%20go%20to%20Odisha%20to%20learn%20pearl%20farming.%20I%20request%20the%20state%20government%20to%20help%20me%20in%20this%20regard%20as%20I%20myself%20have%20seen%20unemployment%20days%20and%20I%20wish%20that%20I%20provide%20job%20opportunities%20to%20the%20unemployed%20with%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Vinod%20Bharti)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708667617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342922%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wondering%20how%20to%20do%20pearl%20farming%20in%20artificial%20ponds%3F%20Rajasthan's%20Vinod%20Bharti%20started%20growing%20oyster%20pearls%20when%20he%20had%20lost%20all%20ways%20of%20livelihood%20and%20today%20earns%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20per%20batch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342922%2Fhow-to-do-pearl-farming-in-artificial-ponds-in-rajasthan-computer-teacher-reaps-huge-profits%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20UPSC%20Mains%20Marksheet%E2%80%99%3A%20IAS%20Officer%20Shares%20Prep%20Lessons%20With%20Memories%20of%20Her%201st%20Failed%20Attempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20failure%20is%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20statement%20rings%20especially%20true%20for%20many%20successful%20individuals%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20civil%20services.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333846%2Fhyderabad-balalatha-mallavarapu-affected-by-polio-crack-upsc-cse-without-coaching-teaches-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%3C%2Fa%3E%20exams%20stand%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20competitive%20and%20challenging%20examinations%20to%20conquer.%20Behind%20the%20triumph%20of%20many%20rank%20holders%20and%20nearly%20all%20officers%2C%20lies%20a%20compelling%20story%20of%20perseverance%20and%20resilience%20amidst%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20story%20is%20that%20of%20Sonal%20Goel%20%E2%80%94%20an%20IAS%20officer%2C%20currently%20serving%20as%20the%20Resident%20Commissioner%20at%20Tripura%20Bhawan%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20She%20secured%20the%20All%20India%20Rank%2013%20in%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20many%20know%20that%20this%20was%20her%20second%20attempt%2C%20as%20she%20fell%20short%20of%20going%20to%20the%20interview%20stage%20by%20a%20few%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonal%20recounted%20this%20story%20alongside%20a%20picture%20of%20her%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%202007%20Mains%20mark%20sheet%2C%20shared%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20She%20reflected%20on%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20her%20selection%20in%20May%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20remarkably%2C%20she%20achieved%20this%20feat%20while%20simultaneously%20pursuing%20her%20LLB%20(Bachelor%20of%20Laws)%20and%20working%20part-time%20as%20a%20Company%20Secretary%20(CS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20had%20low%20marks%20in%20the%20general%20studies%20paper%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%2