-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20battle%20between%20chemical%20and%20organic%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntent%20on%20creating%20a%20solution%20for%20farmers%20to%20increase%20their%20yield%2C%20Akshay%20explored%20the%20options%20that%20lay%20before%20him%20%E2%80%94%20either%20work%20on%20improving%20the%20seed%20quality%20or%20work%20on%20improving%20the%20fertiliser%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20chose%20the%20second%20for%20its%20potential.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20knows%20there%20are%20two%20kinds%20of%20fertilisers%20that%20exist.%20One%20is%20a%20chemical%20fertiliser%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20organic.%20Something%20that%20I%20have%20never%20been%20able%20to%20understand%20is%20why%20people%20still%20use%20chemical%20fertilisers%20when%20they%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20harmful%20effects.%20Also%2C%20why%20haven%E2%80%99t%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340672%2Fjharkhand-farming-rukmani-devi-abusive-marriage-domestic-violence-survivor-learnt-farming-to-earn-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20fertilisers%3C%2Fa%3E%20become%20popular%20in%20spite%20of%20their%20benefits%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20computer%20lab%20of%20his%20college%2C%20Akshay%20began%20looking%20for%20the%20answers.%20But%20the%20facts%20he%20stumbled%20across%20only%20added%20to%20his%20initial%20shock.%20A%202020%20report%20by%20the%20BioMed%20Central%20(BMC)%20Public%20Health%20Journal%20suggested%20around%20385%20million%20people%2C%20particularly%20among%20farmers%20and%20agriculture%20workers%2C%20are%20poisoned%20by%20pesticides%20every%20year.%20It%20also%20accounts%20for%2011%2C000%20deaths%20per%20year.%20Among%20the%20fatalities%2C%20nearly%2060%20percent%20or%206%2C600%20deaths%20per%20year%2C%20occur%20in%20India%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20dying%20due%20to%20chemical%20fertilisers.%20But%20why%20are%20%3Ca%20rel