ing%5C%22%3EJourney%20to%20her%20magic%20garden%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20with%20an%20affinity%20for%20plants%20and%20greenery%2C%20Viji%20has%20been%20fond%20of%20gardening%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20have%20been%20decades%20since%20I%20have%20been%20tending%20to%20a%20garden.%20It%20is%20my%20favourite%20thing%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20a%20full-time%20gardener%2C%20she%20was%20an%20accountant.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20sounds%20like%20two%20different%20worlds%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20gardening%20was%20always%20a%20part%20of%20who%20I%20was.%20When%20my%20first%20child%20was%20born%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20lived%20on%20our%20own.%20So%20one%20of%20us%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313207%2Faravinthan-coimbatore-organic-farm-seed-bank-preserves-rare-varieties-vegetables-pulses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20our%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20raise%20the%20children.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20my%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20putting%20down%20her%20papers%2C%20Viji%E2%80%99s%20mind%20was%20not%20at%20ease.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20create%20and%20leave%20back%20something%20of%20my%20own%20in%20the%20world.%20But%2C%20I%20did%20not%20have%20the%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20with%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20newborn%2C%20the%20young%20mother%20started%20to%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20her%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CTending%20the%20baby%20and%20the%20garden%20gave%20me%20solace%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fflowers-5-1708088457.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%2