r%20digital%20integration%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20activity%20that%20Lenovo%20undertook%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Dream%20India%20Network%2C%20was%20to%20choose%2025%20farmers%20%E2%80%94%2016%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20%E2%80%94%20from%20five%20wards%20and%20convince%20them%20to%20sow%20millets%20in%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20land.%20They%20were%20given%20good-quality%20seeds%20and%20taught%20different%20ways%20to%20revive%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20farmers%20were%20already%20growing%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20self-consumption.%20We%20asked%20them%20to%20try%20growing%20any%20of%20the%20other%20five%20varieties%20in%2050%20cents%20of%20their%20unused%20land%20by%20instilling%20confidence%20that%20we%20would%20market%20it.%20Since%20the%20land%20was%20already%20used%20for%20millet%20cultivation%20earlier%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20problem.%20Furthermore%2C%20millets%20grow%20in%20low-fertility%20soils%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20need%20too%20much%20water.%20They%20just%20need%20timely%20rain%20to%20get%20a%20good%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Saju%20Parackal%2C%20CEO%2C%20Dream%20India%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20tech%20to%20revive%20traditions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IHRD%20College%20students%20volunteer%20alongside%20Lenovo%20volunteers%20oversee%20the%20Tech%20Centre.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo3-1708067458-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0