points%20and%20seed%20banks%20for%20Kanthalloor%20Millets.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456.jpeg%201201w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-500x666.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-768x1023.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-1153x1536.jpeg%201153w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo2-1708067456-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342036%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMillet%20kiosks%20will%20be%20set%20up%20at%20each%20homestay%20in%20Kanthalloor.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Parackal%20says%20they%20are%20creating%20linkages%20with%20exporters%20to%20sell%20millets%20once%20the%20yield%20increases%20and%20are%20also%20working%20with%20the%20Kerala%20Government%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20department%20to%20widen%20the%20processing%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhakrishnan%2C%20a%20farmer%20who%20is%20part%20of%20the%20programme%20and%20former%20president%20of%20Devikulam%20block%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20expressed%20happiness%20at%20the%20initiative.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20traditional%20food%3B%20we%20have%20started%20consuming%20unhealthy%20food%20only%20over%20the%20past%2030%20years.%20It%20came%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20good-quality%20seeds%20to%20sow.%20Lenovo%20helped%20us%20source%20good%20quality%20seeds%2C%20which%20have%20helped%20us%20get%20a%20good%20harvest.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20of%20an%20even%20better%20yield%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20harvest%20produced%20more%20than%201%2C800%20kg%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20company.%20Encouraged%20by%20this%20success%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20involve%2025%20additional%20farmers%2C%20each%20with%20an%20acre%2C%20expanding%20millet%20cultivation%20to%20cover%2075%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELenovo%20volunteers%20helped%20gather%20data%20and%20analyse%20the%20impact%20of%20solutions%2C%20helping%20farmers%20access%20the%20necessary%20apps%2C%20and%20building%20awareness%20for%20market%20linkages.%20They%20are%20also%20providing%20digital%20access%20to%20information%20on%20Government%20programmes%20and%20millet%20cultivation%20methods%20to%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mohandas%20informs%20that%20he%20is%20boosting%20the%20production%20of%20millet%20by%20giving%20subsidies%20to%20124%20farmers%20from%20next%20year.%20Kannamma%20Gopalan%2C%20one%20of%20the%2025%20farmers%20who%20saw%20a%20good%20yield%2C%20hopes%20that%20this%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305138%2Fmasterchef-india-contestant-whips-up-gluten-free-desserts-in-her-house-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epath%20towards%20progress%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20villagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20might%20push%20the%20youngsters%20to%20take%20an%20interest%20in%20farming.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20major%20step%20towards%20progress%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708083184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FLenovo1-1708067454.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lenovo%E2%80%99s%20Work%20fo